OL,5,G1650 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FThe final visit is to The Royal
OL,7,     FOak Inn in Somerset, run by
OL,8,     FSpencer and Gavin. After talking a
OL,9,     Fgood game all week, the guests are
OL,10,     Fshocked to find the standards to
OL,11,     Fbe rather... standard.
OL,12,G1720 Four in a Bed
